---
// UpsellCurso.astro
---
<section class="py-24 bg-[#1a120b] relative overflow-hidden text-center">
  <!-- Decorative Glows -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#B11252]/20 to-transparent rounded-full blur-[100px] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-gradient-to-bl from-[#e6b866]/10 to-transparent rounded-full blur-[100px] translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="mb-16">
      <span class="text-[#e6b866] text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3 block">Curso de Fundamentos</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-white mb-6">Aprende los Fundamentos de la Cábala</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 font-sans text-lg font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        ¿Quieres profundizar en este conocimiento sagrado antes de interpretar tu cálculo completo? Te ofrecemos un curso estructurado en 9 módulos para comprender las bases ancestrales.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 9 Modules Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-16">
      {
        [
          "Qué es la Cábala",
          "El Árbol de la Vida",
          "Árbol Personal",
          "Las 10 Sefirot",
          "Los 22 Senderos",
          "Numerología Sagrada",
          "Cálculos Básicos",
          "Interpretación",
          "Aplicación Práctica"
        ].map((modulo, index) => (
          <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center shadow-lg hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-[#e6b866]/30 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
            <span class="block text-[#e6b866] font-serif font-medium text-2xl mb-2 opacity-50">0{index + 1}</span>
            <p class="text-white font-sans font-medium text-sm md:text-base tracking-wide uppercase">{modulo}</p>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>

    <div>
      <a href="https://sabiduriadealma.com/curso-basico-arbol-de-la-kabala" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#e6b866] to-[#c29851] text-slate-900 font-serif font-semibold tracking-widest text-lg py-4 px-10 rounded-xl shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(230,184,102,0.3)] hover:shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(230,184,102,0.5)] transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
        <span>📖 COMPRAR CURSO AHORA</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
